"content_id": "8251",
"reference_id": 0,
"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "8251: faithfulness, to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8251",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The proper response to God by his covenant people; seen in a steadfast commitment which reflects God's own faithfulness to the covenant. Encouraged in all believers, it is especially important in leaders.</p>\n<h2>Faithfulness is the proper response to God by his covenant people</h2>\n<h3>God's covenant with his people requires faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:3-1Kgs2:4\">1KI 2:3–2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">EXO 19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:32-Deut5:33\">DEU 5:32–5:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:9\">DEU 29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:26\">ISA 1:26</a></p>\n<h3>Faithfulness to God seen as marital fidelity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:20\">HOS 2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:5\">ISA 54:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:2\">JER 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:8\">EZK 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:1\">EPH 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:22-Eph5:25\">EPH 5:22–5:25</a></p>\n<h3>Faithfulness to God reflects God's faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:35\">1SA 2:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:12-1Cor10:13\">1CO 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:14-Heb4:16\">HEB 4:14–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness is seen as steadfast commitment to God</h2>\n<h3>In unwavering devotion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:5\">MIC 4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14-Josh24:15\">JOS 24:14–24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:62\">LUK 9:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>In obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:13\">DEU 11:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:9\">EZK 18:9</a></p>\n<h3>In service</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:24\">1SA 12:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:9\">2CH 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:10-2Chr34:12\">2CH 34:10–34:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:4-2Kgs22:7\">2KI 22:4–22:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:15\">EZK 44:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek48:11\">EZK 48:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:12\">1TI 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>In giving</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:12\">2CH 31:12</a> <em>Faithfulness to God is expressed in giving to him for the benefit of others</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:1–8:5</a></p>\n<h3>In prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:17\">1TH 5:17</a></p>\n<h3>In patient endurance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:11-2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:11–2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:36\">HEB 10:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:10\">REV 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:12\">REV 14:12</a></p>\n<h3>In fulfilling vows</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num30:2\">NUM 30:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:21-Deut23:23\">DEU 23:21–23:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:25\">PSA 22:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:8\">PSA 61:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:4\">ECC 5:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:9\">JON 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness is especially important in leaders</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:1-1Cor4:2\">1CO 4:1–4:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3\">3JN 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:21\">EXO 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:13-1Tim4:16\">1TI 4:13–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:20\">1TI 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:13-2Tim1:14\">2TI 1:13–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:2\">2TI 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1-2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:1–4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Encouragements to faithfulness</h2>\n<h3>The call to faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:1\">GAL 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13\">EPH 6:13</a></p>\n<h3>God watches over the faithful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:10\">PSA 97:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:23\">PSA 31:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:28\">PSA 37:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:2\">PSA 86:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:8\">PRO 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>God rewards faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:23\">1SA 26:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">MAT 25:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:17\">LUK 19:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:6\">PSA 101:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:20\">PRO 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:45-Matt24:47\">MAT 24:45–24:47</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:42-Luke12:44\">LUK 12:42–12:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:6-2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:6–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:4\">REV 20:4</a></p>\n<h2>Lack of faithfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:1\">HOS 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:1\">PSA 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:8\">PSA 78:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:37\">PSA 78:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:2\">HOS 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:7\">HOS 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:1\">HOS 9:1</a></p>",
